Subject: drm/i915/crt: fix DPMS standby and suspend mode handling
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 4a8dece21eea0ad6aca442272673d48693cd93b4
Patch-mainline: v3.7-rc6

PCH platforms and VLV should map DPMS standby and suspend modes to off, but
due to a buggy reversed comparison this is done on pre-PCH platforms
instead.

